## Project Objective
The objective of this project is to practice project management using industry-standard tools including Trello and GitHub.

## Project Scope
This project includes:
- Task management using Trello
- Document version control using GitHub
- Team collaboration and task assignment
- Risk management and project scheduling

## Expected Outcomes
- A fully functional Trello board with tasks and assignments
- A GitHub repository with project documents
- A final report explaining the benefits of both tools

